## 12. Utility Functions and Code Quality Improvements

Several helper functions were added to improve code clarity:

```rust
// Toroidal distance calculation
fn toroidal_delta(a: f32, b: f32, extent: f32) -> f32 {
    let mut delta = b - a;
    let half = extent * 0.5;
    if delta > half {
        delta -= extent;
    } else if delta < -half {
        delta += extent;
    }
